headline: Mountaingate Capital Partners with Podean and Commerce Canal to Form the Largest Independent Global Marketplace Focused Agency
summary: DENVER, August 20, 2025--Mountaingate Capital ("Mountaingate") today announced that Mountaingate Fund III has made its first investment, partnering with Podean, a globally recognized marketplace agency, and Commerce Canal, a leader in marketplace strategy and operations. headline: Shower gel ad banned for ‘offensive stereotype’ about black skin
summary: An advertisement for shower gel has been banned after regulators warned that it used a racial stereotype that black skin was “problematic” and that white skin was “superior”.
